Source.Name: purpose
Source.Summary: Framework for providing abstractions to get the developer's purposes fulfilled.
Source.Description: This framework offers the possibility to create integrate services and actions on any application without having to implement them specifically. Purpose will offer them mechanisms to list the different alternatives to execute given the requested action type and will facilitate components so that all the plugins can receive all the information they need.
